## Installation
git clone https://github.com/suraj1724/Shopping-Portal.git
cd shopping-portal
npm install

## PORT=4000/ localhost
DB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/shopping_portal


## API Endpoints
GET /: Retrieve all products.       http://localhost:4000/
DELETE /product/:id: Delete a product by ID. 
GET    /product/:id: Retrieve a product by ID.  
GET    /product/updated-last-24-hours Retrieve a product which updated within 24 hours
PUT   /product/:id: Update a product by ID.     http://localhost:4000/product/66068a8158fa6e8eb50971e2 (edit the values using JSON data format)
GET /product/status/:status Get products by status   http://localhost:4000/product/status/pending (pending/completed)
POST /product: Create a new product.    http://localhost:4000/product
                                       JSON DATA:
                                                { "title": "Mens Cotton Jackets and cloths", "description":"great outerwear jackets for Spring/Autumn/Winter, suitable for many occasions, such as working, hiking, camping, mountain/rock climbing, cycling, traveling or other outdoors. Good gift choice for you or your family member. A warm hearted love to Father, husband or son in this thanksgiving or Christmas Day."  }


 

## Technologies Used
Node.js
Express
MongoDB